          "description": "Syntax specification of the instruction. `[fF]\\d+` is interpreted as the field with index `i` of the instruction. Other characters are interpreted literally. Ex: `F0 F3 F1 (F2)`",
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    },
    "Range_of_Integer": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["end", "start"],
